Melchana: Slagging comm officer... If I ever get my paws on you... 
(she re-opened a commline to the Autobot ship) Autobot Ship, this is 
Tripredacus fighter Hellgate requesting permission to land. (she 
switched frequencies to talk with her brother aboard the Hidden One) 
GESPER!!!!! Tell your goody-goody friends to allow me to land or I'll 
pull on the freaking triggers and I won't stop until that ship is 
so slagging ground-levelled!!!!!

The Hellgate slowly came into firing position with the ship, but the 
weapons were still down.

Gesper: Alright, sister... JetV, I think my sister wants to land. Care 
to tell her she can?
